    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“我们以前聊过这个，不是吗？”阴影在门口说道。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >困在螺旋之中，劳拉必须在潜意识的深处开辟出一条道路，否则就会沉入虚无。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301370/extras/45bc3be4c73e2477a7a9e7f4941e7dab.poster.avif?t=1772402448\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301370/extras/45bc3be4c73e2477a7a9e7f4941e7dab.webm?t=1772402448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301370/extras/45bc3be4c73e2477a7a9e7f4941e7dab.mp4?t=1772402448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >复古生存恐怖</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在探索一座荒废的小镇时寻找物资并生存下去，恐怖的怪物将在每个角落纠缠着你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301370/extras/db14e4e497793fe8fcb5cf2dd35fb258.poster.avif?t=1772402448\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301370/extras/db14e4e497793fe8fcb5cf2dd35fb258.webm?t=1772402448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301370/extras/db14e4e497793fe8fcb5cf2dd35fb258.mp4?t=1772402448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >心理噩梦</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >环境会随着每一次循环而改变。当你挖掘出曾经深埋的创伤时，世界将变得愈发腐朽。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301370/extras/c3dff7b95d9431734dc94f907d4862f3.poster.avif?t=1772402448\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301370/extras/c3dff7b95d9431734dc94f907d4862f3.webm?t=1772402448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301370/extras/c3dff7b95d9431734dc94f907d4862f3.mp4?t=1772402448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >杀出重围</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >配备了各种武器，劳拉在面对追捕者时并非完全无助。在噩梦中战斗并赢回你的生命，或者在尝试中死去。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301370/extras/5f9ddd21d500a65bb97900754c6ae322.poster.avif?t=1772402448\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301370/extras/5f9ddd21d500a65bb97900754c6ae322.webm?t=1772402448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301370/extras/5f9ddd21d500a65bb97900754c6ae322.mp4?t=1772402448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解开谜题，揭开真相</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有些真相近在眼前；有些则需要你找回记忆的关键碎片才能解锁。解开这些谜题以开启新区域，并揭开你所遗忘的痛苦记忆的面纱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
